{
  "stem": "719.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was really, literally, money strolling on the streets, and nobody would worry about it, because the German mark was important.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And also, the-- the wheeling and dealing started of-- with food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And because we had coal mines-- this is one interesting situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother had a brother living in a bigger city somewhere, not far where Jack was born, in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they established a ghetto much earlier than where I lived, 'cause smaller towns were in touch with non-Jewish farmers.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We could deal something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We could manage to get a little bit of food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But what we did have-- coal to heat, to-- to bring heat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And a piece-- a brick of coal looks like a piece of diamond.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It sparkles.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I don't know if you ever saw coal coming out from the coal mines, from underneath.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we got a hold of something like that, I don't know how my mother tried to send it to her brother, at least to keep warm.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because if you hungry and cold, at least-- well, one thing we did have is heat in the house.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a big fireplace, and they put as much coal as they could to keep it warm all night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I met my parents, when we arrived, my father was an optimist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think maybe he didn't want to show it to me. 'Cause I remember later on, later on when food was a lot scarce and he-- there wasn't enough to eat, he used to say, you go ahead and eat.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I already ate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm positive he wasn't eating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was either fasting or leaving the food for his child.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm positive, because he always used to say, well, I'm not hungry.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll eat later.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
